  "title": "Score Engine v1 — canonical contract-test fixtures",
  "description": "Closes Verify Blocker B1. Every row is a contract-test input/output pair for the score-engine implementation. PR-blocking test `pnpm test score-engine` asserts `score_v1(input) === expected_output` for every row, AND that the verdict-rule priority order matches PRD §10 (Blocker override evaluated before score-band). Formula: `score = max(0, round_half_even(100 - Σ weights[severity]))`. Weights: Blocker 30, Critical 18, Major 7, Minor 2, Polish 0.5. Thresholds: fail_below=70, pass_with_fixes_min=70, pass_with_fixes_max=94, pass_min=95. Rounding: half-to-even (banker's).",
  "engine_version": "v1",
  "schema_under_test": "score_engine.v1.json",
  "rows": [
