        "verdict_rule_triggered": "score_in_pass_with_fixes_band",
        "notes": "18 + 7 + 2 + 2 + 0.5 + 0.5 = 30. 100 − 30 = 70. Edge-of-band on the lower side. Verifies the inclusive-min boundary."
